	<Name>Great Circus Mystery Starring Mickey & Minnie, The (USA)</Name>
	<plot>Overview:The Great Circus Mystery Starring Mickey &amp; Minnie (JP: Mickey to Minnie Magical Adventure 2) is a Disney-themed video game starring Mickey and Minnie Mouse. The duo track down the missing people at the circus, tracking them across six different stages. Mickey and Minnie have the unique ability to change outfits during the game to use different powers. The player can choose to play as either Mickey or Minnie, the latter becoming playable for the first time.Though not clear in the US/European title, the game is a sequel to the 1992 SNES game Magical Quest Starring Mickey Mouse. It saw a GBA rerelease in 2003 titled Disney's Magical Quest 2 Starring Mickey &amp; Minnie, which made the Magical Quest connection clearer.			</plot>
